Fair of the DragonfairnM0none12346781783465searchvar2100006*09*all***04*03*This fair has everything to please: amusements, tournaments and even a public theater. If you like seafood, you will find it available all around the clock. A gold statue of a huge dragon greets you at the entrance; no one is guarding it, but the weight of it prevents anyone from entertaining thoughts about stealing it.